<br>
Absolutely, without question.  But then, this can be applied to any class.<br>
<br>
I could define two variables: situational awareness and adaptation.<br>
<br>
The excellent mage will understand both, and contribute to a group.  The slacker mage will go oom in basic xp groups.<br>
<br>
I've seen both just like everyone else.  The former makes a good group great.  The latter gives our class a bad rep.<br>
<br>
All this said, I'm not sure of the intention of the original post.<br>
