Anyone who has completed the Trial of Execution and attempted the others will tell you that PoP includes content that demands players at the bleeding edge of game skill levels. Luck has its part, but the fact that you can see incredibly well equipped players fail while lesser-endowed groups succeed is testament to the new demanding and skillful encounters.<br>
<br>
You gave your point of view which was what I was after.<br>
