<br>
We always know exactly where the enemy is, and stay right on top of them.  Compare this to, say, Rangers, who always spend a few seconds spinning and running around whenever the enemy moves.<br>
<br>
We don't have to med, and rarely need to rest.  You can sit down for a while, and regain mana or read magazines, or whatever else it is you do, and no one thinks you are slacking.  We are on task!<br>
<br>
We take the aggro so you don't have to.<br>
<br>
Admittedly we sometimes act kind of stupidly, but this is strictly according to the Standard Operating Procedures Manual, and we really have no choice about it.  But how many Rangers are even stupider?<br>
<br>
You're never alone as a master of the elements!<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Lobaner</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
